[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0921","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0921.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1074","title":"Webmin 密码暴力破解漏洞","description":"Webmin 0.5 之前版本存在认证机制缺陷，对有效用户名的登录密码尝试次数未作限制，远程攻击者可利用该漏洞对目标系统实施暴力枚举攻击，通过不断尝试常用或弱口令来猜测系统管理员密码，从而获取 Webmin 管理面板的访问权限并最终控制服务器。该漏洞影响 Webmin 0.5 及更早版本，属于高风险缺陷，攻击门槛较低，且无需提前获取任何认证凭据。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1074"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.017","remediation":"立即升级 Webmin 至 0.5 或更高版本，该版本已限制同一用户名的密码尝试次数。如无法升级，可在 Webmin 前端配置额外认证模块（如 fail2ban）限制登录频率，并在防火墙层面将 Webmin 管理端口（默认 10000）仅对可信 IP 开放，同时启用强密码策略作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9138","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/98","http://www.webmin.com/webmin/changes.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1074.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1074","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1074.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1074.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1074.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gwfg-h74f-g6gq/GHSA-gwfg-h74f-g6gq.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/robinzixuan/attackmap/blob/3e50ba1e011308b7d6ea18a627132f0a357f36c0/Asia/bruteresult.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000988.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--39926f99-82f5-4fec-ad30-6de2b1dd04dc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0921.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0921.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0893","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0893.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1043","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.0/5.5 NNTP 和 SMTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.0 和 5.5 版本在处理畸形的 NNTP（网络新闻传输协议）数据或 SMTP（简单邮件传输协议）数据时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标邮件服务器发送特制的畸形数据包触发服务进程错误，导致 Exchange 服务崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.0 和 5.5，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1043"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.187","remediation":"将 Microsoft Exchange Server 升级至 5.5 Service Pack 3（SP3）或更高版本（Exchange 5.0 用户需先迁移至 5.5 再安装 SP3）。如无法升级，可在服务器管理中禁用 NNTP 虚拟服务器服务，并在防火墙策略中限制 TCP 25（SMTP）和 TCP 119（NNTP）端口的访问来源为可信 IP 段。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-007","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1043","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1043.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hjv9-q8gw-pmgm/GHSA-hjv9-q8gw-pmgm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88091/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1043.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0893.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0890","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0890.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1042","title":"Cisco Resource Manager 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco Resource Manager (CRM) 1.0 和 1.1 版本存在信息泄露漏洞。由于程序创建的日志文件及临时文件权限设置为全局可读，本地攻击者可利用该缺陷读取这些文件，从而获取用户ID、密码及SNMP团体字符串等敏感凭据信息。此漏洞影响CRM 1.0和1.1版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，CVSS评分1.2，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1042"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.067","remediation":"升级 Cisco Resource Manager 至 1.2 或更高版本以修复默认文件权限问题；对手动创建的日志目录和临时文件目录执行 chmod 600 或 640，仅允许 CRM 服务账户读写；通过文件系统 ACL 限制本地非授权用户访问 /var/log/crm 及临时目录；定期审计日志文件权限配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/crmtmp-pub.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1042","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1042.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qqff-qxc6-9qw5/GHSA-qqff-qxc6-9qw5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87012/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0890.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0889","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0889.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1035","title":"Microsoft IIS HTTP GET 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 及 4.0 版本（x86 和 Alpha 平台）在处理畸形的 HTTP GET 请求时存在缺陷，远程未经认证的攻击者可向目标 Web 服务器发送特制的 GET 请求，导致 IIS 服务进程挂起，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程触发，影响运行 IIS 3.0/4.0 的 Windows NT 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。官方建议升级至更高版 IIS 版本或部署安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1035"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:34.207","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS98-019 提供的对应平台热修补丁（IIS 3.0/4.0 for x86/Alpha），或升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 更高版本。由于 IIS 3.0 和 4.0 均已停止技术支持多年，强烈建议迁移至现代受支持的操作系统及 IIS 版本（如 Windows Server 2022 + IIS 10），从根本上消除此漏洞风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q192/2/96.asp","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-019","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1823","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1035.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1035.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1035","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1035.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1035.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1035.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rpfw-6596-9q7g/GHSA-rpfw-6596-9q7g.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1035.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1035.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0889.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0579","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0579.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0815","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SNMP Agent 内存泄漏拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SNMP 服务代理存在内存泄漏漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统 SNMP 服务发送大量查询请求，导致系统内存资源被持续消耗直至耗尽，最终造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP5 之前版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。安装 SP5 及以上版本补丁可修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0815"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.917","remediation":"升级 Windows NT 4.0 至 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本，SP5 已修复 SNMP Agent 的内存泄漏问题。对于无法升级的系统，可在防火墙规则中限制对 UDP 端口 161 的访问，仅允许受信任的管理站发起 SNMP 查询，以降低远程攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q196/2/70.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1974","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A952"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0579.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0572","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0572.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0808","title":"ISC DHCP 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC DHCP 服务器（dhcpd）1.0 和 2.0 版本存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标 DHCP 服务器发送包含超长选项字段的恶意数据包，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务，甚至可能利用该漏洞执行任意代码。该漏洞影响大量使用 ISC DHCP 服务的网络环境，攻击条件简单，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0808"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.993","remediation":"建议立即升级 ISC DHCP 至 3.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复 dhcpd 1.0/2.0 中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙上限制对 DHCP 服务器 UDP 67/68 端口的访问，仅允许受信任的子网段通信作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-053.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101925960&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0572.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0002","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0001","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD TCP/IP 实现拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BSD 衍生系统（包括 FreeBSD、OpenBSD 等）的 TCP/IP 协议栈实现中的 ip_input.c 文件存在输入验证漏洞（CWE-20），未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致目标系统崩溃或挂起，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多个 BSD 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0001"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:13.977","remediation":"立即将 FreeBSD 升级至 2.2.8 及以上版本，或将 OpenBSD 升级至 2.3 及以上版本；对于无法升级的系统，下载并安装对应厂商发布的 ip_input.c 补丁。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙或路由器上配置 ACL，丢弃入站 IP 分片包（若业务不需要分片功能），或部署支持 IP 分片校验的入侵防御系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata23.html#tcpfix","http://www.osvdb.org/5707","https://github.com/MarcusGutierrez/complex-vulnerabilities"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0001","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0001","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD TCP/IP 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 及 OpenBSD 等 BSD 衍生系统 TCP/IP 协议栈实现中的 ip_input.c 文件存在输入验证不当漏洞（CWE-20），远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致目标系统内核崩溃或死锁，进而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD、OpenBSD 等多个 BSD 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。建议升级至修复版本或应用厂商发布的安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0001"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:13.977","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.8 或 3.0 及以上版本，OpenBSD 升级至 2.4 及以上版本。临时缓解措施可在边界防火墙上过滤畸形 IP 分片包，或禁用不必要的 raw socket 处理功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata23.html#tcpfix","http://www.osvdb.org/5707","https://github.com/MarcusGutierrez/complex-vulnerabilities"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0200","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0200.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0477","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 远程文件上传与执行漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0 的 Expression Evaluator 组件中 openfile.cfm 文件未对远程用户的文件操作进行有效权限限制，导致存在访问控制缺陷。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞向服务器上传任意文件，进而实现文件显示、删除或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 ColdFusion Server 4.0 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0477"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.877","remediation":"升级到 Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0.1 或更高版本，或移除/限制对 openfile.cfm 的匿名访问权限，通过 Web 服务器配置（如 IIS 或 Apache）禁止外部直接访问该文件。如无法升级，可在应用层实现对 openfile.cfm 的 IP 白名单访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/115","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0200.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0198","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0198.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0455","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Expression Evaluator 远程文件读取删除漏洞","description":"ColdFusion 的 Expression Evaluator 示例应用（exprcalc.cfm）存在未授权访问漏洞，由于未对服务器资源访问进行适当限制，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接访问该示例页面读取或删除服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Adobe ColdFusion 服务器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0455"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.050","remediation":"删除或移除 ColdFusion 服务器上的 `exprcalc.cfm` 及整个 `/cfdocs/` 示例应用目录；升级到 Adobe 官方仍在维护的 ColdFusion (2021/2023) 最新版本；在 Web 服务器层（IIS/Apache/Nginx）通过访问控制规则禁止外部访问 `/CFIDE/` 和 `/cfdocs/` 目录，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/115"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0198.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0687","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0687.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0892","title":"Netscape Communicator 动态字体处理缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.7 之前版本在处理动态字体时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可构造一个长度字段值小于字体实际尺寸的恶意字体文件，诱使用户通过受影响浏览器访问包含该字体的网页，触发缓冲区溢出，可能导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 Netscape Communicator 浏览器系列，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0892"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.440","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.7 或更高版本，该版本修复了动态字体解析中的缓冲区边界检查缺陷。如无法升级，可在浏览器设置中禁用动态字体渲染功能，并考虑迁移至仍在维护的替代浏览器以减少风险暴露。通过防火墙阻断外部字体服务器连接也可作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0892"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0687.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0949","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1109","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail 8.10.0 ETRN命令处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.10.0 之前版本中存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 SMTP 服务器发送大量 ETRN 命令后立即断开连接来触发该漏洞。当攻击者断开连接后，Sendmail 进程仍会继续处理已接收的 ETRN 命令，持续消耗服务器资源，导致邮件服务响应缓慢甚至崩溃，影响正常邮件收发功能。该漏洞利用简单，无需认证，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1109"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.347","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.10.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 ETRN 命令处理中连接断开后继续处理导致资源耗尽的问题。如无法升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中限制 ETRN 命令来源 IP，或通过防火墙限制 SMTP 端口入站连接频次作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94632241202626&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94780566911948&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7760.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/904","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19701","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1109","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1109.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/sendmail_etrn_dos.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000955.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1109.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1682","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1682.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0997","title":"WU-FTPD FTP Conversion 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 2.4.2至2.6.2版本中启用了FTP文件转换功能时存在命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过上传包含特殊畸形文件名的文件，该文件名在传输过程中被作为参数传递给转换程序（如tar或uncompress），从而导致任意命令在服务器端执行。该漏洞影响多版本WU-FTPD服务器，CVSS评分7.5，危害等级高危。攻击者无需身份认证，仅需具备FTP上传权限即可触发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0997"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.343","remediation":"升级至 wu-ftpd 2.6.3 或更高版本以修复此漏洞；若无法升级，在 ftpaccess 配置文件中关闭 conversion 功能，注释或移除相关 conversion 规则，并限制匿名用户上传目录不可执行转换操作。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 tar、uncompress 等转换程序的 setuid 权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/2003/dsa-377","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20563","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/