W5/GWWEB.EXE 的访问权限以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94571433731824&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1006","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1006.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j6r8-2wq6-f58q/GHSA-j6r8-2wq6-f58q.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/groupwise_web_interface_help_hole.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88366/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1006.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0852.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0850","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0850.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1005","title":"Novell GroupWise GWWEB.EXE 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Novell GroupWise 邮件系统的 Web 服务器组件 GWWEB.EXE 存在目录遍历漏洞。由于对 HELP 参数输入过滤不严，远程攻击者无需身份认证，可通过包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 HTTP 请求绕过路径限制，读取服务器上任意 .htm 扩展名的文件，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 GroupWise 5.2 及 5.5 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","